I, JAMES C DRAKE, Clerk of the Circuit Court of the United States, for the Western District of Washington, do hereby certify that the foregoing attached papers constitute the JUDGMENT ROLL in the foregoing entitled cause, No. 1313 wherein In Re: Application of L.J. Urann, Habeas Corpus Plaintiff and
